## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the full complexity of historical events and perspectives. Additionally, the historical context of racial discrimination is vast and multifaceted, making it challenging to cover all aspects comprehensively in a brief report. Further research into primary historical documents and scholarly analyses would provide a more nuanced understanding of the topic.